part of being human.

11
00:00:53,791 --> 00:00:54,666
You killed...

12
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:56,333
her...

13
00:00:56,416 --> 00:00:58,000
Teresa...

14
00:00:59,250 --> 00:01:00,958
Teresa.

15
00:01:12,125 --> 00:01:14,666
