31
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:24,500
I'll kill you!

32
00:03:25,625 --> 00:03:26,958
Priscilla.

33
00:03:28,708 --> 00:03:29,375
No...

34
00:03:29,458 --> 00:03:31,166
