I won't forgive you!

39
00:03:58,250 --> 00:03:59,791
You're gonna die!

40
00:04:01,416 --> 00:04:02,875
By my sword!

41
00:04:12,083 --> 00:04:13,583
You're mine!

42
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,875
Wow...

43
00:04:43,958 --> 00:04:45,333
Not bad.

44
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,291
Clare.

45
00:05:08,333 --> 00:05:09,916
Unbelievable.

46
00:05:13,666 --> 00:05:14,750
Incredible...

47
00:05:14,833 --> 00:05:16,541
How'd she do that?

48
00:05:17,875 --> 00:05:19,291
It's impossible.

49
00:05:19,375 --> 00:05:21,791
They've both gone
beyond our control.

50
00:05:27,916 --> 00:05:29,666
Clare.

51
00:05:29,750 --> 00:05:31,541
Priscilla.

52
00:05:31,625 --> 00:05:35,875
Why...? What's the matter with
them- why are they fighting...?

53
00:05:35,958 --> 00:05:37,500
Just stop.

54
00:05:37,583 --> 00:05:38,666
Clare...

55
00:05:38,750 --> 00:05:40,166
Priscilla...

56
00:05:40,250 --> 00:05:42,166
Please stop!

57
00:06:22,333 --> 00:06:23,791
That all you've got?

58
00:06:26,041 --> 00:06:27,750
Let her go!

59
00:06:38,541 --> 00:06:39,416
Wait a minute...

60
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:40,458
You're an imposter.

61
00:06:40,541 --> 00:06:42,916
You're not Teresa.

62
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:45,083
