charade once and for all.

69
00:07:16,541 --> 00:07:18,333
Teresa.

70
00:08:33,416 --> 00:08:35,833
You killed Teresa...

71
00:08:40,083 --> 00:08:41,000
Clare.

72
00:08:42,375 --> 00:08:43,500
Clare.

73
00:08:44,875 --> 00:08:45,916
Clare...

74
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:48,708
Clare...

75
00:08:50,291 --> 00:08:51,291
