87
00:09:14,875 --> 00:09:15,750
Clare...

88
00:09:15,833 --> 00:09:16,916
I know...

89
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,416
I know Priscilla murdered
someone who was

90
00:09:18,500 --> 00:09:20,208
very special to you...

91
00:09:20,291 --> 00:09:21,541
but...

92
00:09:21,625 --> 00:09:24,125
Priscilla's entire family
was slaughtered by Yoma,

93
00:09:24,208 --> 00:09:25,625
just like mine!

94
00:09:25,708 --> 00:09:27,583
And it doesn't stop with us.

95
00:09:27,666 --> 00:09:31,375
Everyone has been affected
by this somehow.

96
00:09:31,458 --> 00:09:32,500
Don't you see...

97
00:09:32,583 --> 00:09:33,916
We shouldn't be
fighting each other,

98
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:36,208
we're all lucky to be alive...

99
00:09:36,291 --> 00:09:37,833
Please Clare...

100
00:09:37,916 --> 00:09:40,375
I beg you...

101
00:09:40,458 --> 00:09:44,583
Please...! You've got to try and
keep yourself from awakening!

102
00:09:44,666 --> 00:09:45,666
If you kill Priscilla,

103
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:48,708
then you're no different
than the Yoma!

104
00:09:48,791 --> 00:09:50,416
Please don't do it!

105
00:09:52,291 --> 00:09:54,583
You took her from me...

106
00:09:54,666 --> 00:09:55,500
Teresa...

107
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:57,416
Teresa...

108
00:09:58,125 --> 00:09:59,625
Teresa...

109
00:09:59,708 --> 00:10:01,791
You...

110
00:10:01,875 --> 00:10:04,500
You killed her.

111
00:10:04,583 --> 00:10:06,333
You killed her!

112
00:10:06,416 --> 00:10:07,250
Clare...!

113
00:10:07,333 --> 00:10:08,916
No!

114
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:11,166
Raki.

115
00:10:11,250 --> 00:10:12,375
Please...

116
00:10:12,458 --> 00:10:14,208
You can't become a Yoma!

117
00:10:14,291 --> 00:10:15,125
You can fight it.

118
00:10:15,208 --> 00:10:17,041
I know you have it in you!

119
00:10:27,125 --> 00:10:28,458
Her aura just dropped!

120
00:10:28,541 --> 00:10:29,708
Please Clare...

121
00:10:29,791 --> 00:10:31,291
You've gotta be strong!

122
00:10:31,375 --> 00:10:33,583
Don't you remember
the promise we made?

123
00:10:33,666 --> 00:10:36,958
That no matter what
we would meet again.

124
00:10:37,041 --> 00:10:39,500
My promise to you
has kept me alive...

125
00:10:39,583 --> 00:10:42,833
it's the only reason I continued
fighting when I felt weak...

126
00:10:42,916 --> 00:10:44,000
I...

127
00:10:44,083 --> 00:10:47,083
I just wanted to see you again.

128
00:10:47,166 --> 00:10:49,416
I want us to be like we were...

129
00:10:49,500 --> 00:10:50,958
Clare...

130
00:10:51,041 --> 00:10:53,166
I love you with all my heart...

131
00:10:53,250 --> 00:10:54,833
Please don't turn into a Yoma.

132
00:10:54,916 --> 00:10:56,708
Don't leave me all alone.

133
00:10:59,916 --> 00:11:01,250
I promise...

134
00:11:01,333 --> 00:11:02,875
this time I'll protect
you like I should have

135
00:11:02,958 --> 00:11:04,500
from the beginning...

136
00:11:04,583 --> 00:11:09,500
so you can live the rest of
your life as a human being!

137
00:11:09,583 --> 00:11:11,375
...live a human life.

138
00:11:13,708 --> 00:11:15,083
Ra...

139
00:11:15,166 --> 00:11:17,916
ki.

140
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,083
Yes Clare?

141
00:11:21,125 --> 00:11:23,166
I can't...

142
00:11:23,250 --> 00:11:23,958
stop...

143
00:11:24,041 --> 00:11:26,166
it...

144
00:11:26,250 --> 00:11:27,416
There's nothing...

145
00:11:27,500 --> 00:11:29,166
I can do...

146
00:11:31,875 --> 00:11:32,500
Oh no...

147
00:11:32,583 --> 00:11:33,875
Raki!

148
00:11:48,708 --> 00:11:49,666
Jean no!

149
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,041
Jean...

150
00:11:54,125 --> 00:11:55,625
why...?

151
00:11:56,833 --> 00:11:59,666
You didn't run away
this time...

152
00:11:59,750 --> 00:12:01,125
Well done.

153
00:12:03,583 --> 00:12:04,875
Jean...

154
00:12:04,958 --> 00:12:06,041
Why did you...

155
00:12:06,125 --> 00:12:07,500
do this?

156
00:12:07,583 --> 00:12:08,791
It's the opposite...

157
00:12:08,875 --> 00:12:10,500
of what happened before...

158
00:12:10,583 --> 00:12:11,916
Right Clare?

159
00:12:14,208 --> 00:12:18,375
Do you remember that...?
When I had awakened...

160
00:12:18,458 --> 00:12:20,750
you were able to
bring me back to humanity.

161
00:12:22,125 --> 00:12:23,750
We have to reverse it.

162
00:12:23,833 --> 00:12:26,708
Now this is my chance
to return the favor...

163
00:12:26,791 --> 00:12:30,041
I am forever
in your debt Clare.

164
00:12:30,125 --> 00:12:31,916
Revert back...

165
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:34,500
I know you can do it.

166
00:12:34,583 --> 00:12:36,208
Just like before...

167
00:12:36,291 --> 00:12:39,625
synchronize your
Yoki aura with mine.

168
00:12:39,708 --> 00:12:41,250
Focus Clare...

169
00:12:41,333 --> 00:12:46,041
Focus and I'll pull your
aura back to the good side.

170
00:12:46,125 --> 00:12:48,375
You and I pulled it
off once before...

171
00:12:48,458 --> 00:12:50,708
there's no reason
we can't do it again.

172
00:12:50,791 --> 00:12:51,958
No...

173
00:12:52,041 --> 00:12:54,541
If we do that
you're going to die...

174
00:12:54,625 --> 00:12:56,375
Get away from me...

175
00:12:56,458 --> 00:12:57,916
and save yourself!

176
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,708
It's not too late!

177
00:12:59,791 --> 00:13:01,125
Listen...

178
00:13:01,208 --> 00:13:04,916
These are mortal wounds
I will not recover from...

179
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:07,541
There's no hope for me...

180
00:13:07,625 --> 00:13:09,416
So at least allow
me to use what's

181
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:11,791
left of my life to aid you...

182
00:13:11,875 --> 00:13:14,250
I wouldn't want it
any other way.

183
00:13:14,333 --> 00:13:15,125
Jean...

184
00:13:15,208 --> 00:13:16,541
Damn you.

185
00:13:16,625 --> 00:13:17,833
Let's just do it...

186
00:13:17,916 --> 00:13:19,583
Match your Yoki aura!

187
00:13:26,083 --> 00:13:27,583
Jean...

188
00:13:27,666 --> 00:13:30,916
Stop it...! There's no point in
you going through with this...

189
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:33,041
You don't owe me anything...

190
00:13:33,125 --> 00:13:36,250
Don't sacrifice your
own life for my sake!

191
00:13:36,333 --> 00:13:38,458
Damn it Clare,
I need you to focus!

192
00:13:38,541 --> 00:13:39,333
Don't do it!

193
00:13:39,416 --> 00:13:40,375
Stop!

194
00:13:40,458 --> 00:13:42,083
Clare!

195
00:13:42,166 --> 00:13:43,458
Stop it Jean...

196
00:13:43,541 --> 00:13:46,875
Even if you succeed and
revert me back to a human,

197
00:13:46,958 --> 00:13:50,041
there is nothing in this world
left for me to live for.

198
00:13:50,125 --> 00:13:53,083
If I can't kill Priscilla,
then I may as well die.

199
00:13:53,166 --> 00:13:54,625
Clare!

200
00:13:54,708 --> 00:13:56,875
There will be plenty of time
to find something to live

201
00:13:56,958 --> 00:13:59,125
for once you revert back...

202
00:13:59,208 --> 00:14:00,958
Don't you forget...

203
00:14:01,041 --> 00:14:04,666
There are people in this world
that want to see you live...

204
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:07,958
And there are those who have
put their faith in you.

205
00:14:14,500 --> 00:14:15,666
The truth is...

206
00:14:15,750 --> 00:14:18,250
I am one of those people.

207
00:14:18,333 --> 00:14:19,583
No...

208
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:22,750
Just live...

209
00:14:22,833 --> 00:14:25,041
Please Clare.

210
00:14:25,125 --> 00:14:28,333
I'm glad that we were friends.

211
00:14:28,416 --> 00:14:29,500
Jean...

212
00:14:29,583 --> 00:14:31,583
don't die!

213
00:15:00,958 --> 00:15:04,250
No...

214
00:15:04,333 --> 00:15:06,166
Why did you do that?

215
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:16,291
No Jean...

216
00:15:27,333 --> 00:15:30,958
I haven't been that
entertained in quite a while.

217
00:15:31,041 --> 00:15:32,208
It's you...

218
00:15:32,291 --> 00:15:33,375
I should've known...

219
00:15:33,458 --> 00:15:36,375
Isley

220
00:15:36,458 --> 00:15:38,250
The child's unstable...

221
00:15:38,333 --> 00:15:41,208
though I have no intention
of letting her go yet.

222
00:15:41,291 --> 00:15:43,458
That's why I'm
taking her with me.

223
00:15:47,625 --> 00:15:50,208
I've lost my appetite for
violence after watching

224
00:15:50,291 --> 00:15:52,000
these two go at it.

225
00:15:52,083 --> 00:15:53,958
To continue the bloodshed...

226
00:15:54,041 --> 00:15:56,500
would be uncivilized...

227
00:15:56,583 --> 00:15:58,375
Wouldn't you agree?

228
00:15:59,916 --> 00:16:03,541
Let's leave things as they
are for the time being...

229
00:16:03,625 --> 00:16:07,208
And Raki, I assure you
we will meet again someday.

230
00:16:07,291 --> 00:16:08,625
Keep hold of your sword.

231
00:16:08,708 --> 00:16:10,666
It will serve you well.

232
00:16:13,083 --> 00:16:15,500
His aura...

233
00:16:15,583 --> 00:16:17,708
It was overwhelming.

234
00:16:17,791 --> 00:16:20,041
So that was the Silver King.

235
00:16:20,125 --> 00:16:21,041
God damn...

236
00:16:21,125 --> 00:16:22,958
Everyone's a monster.

237
00:16:23,041 --> 00:16:23,958
Indeed...

238
00:16:24,041 --> 00:16:25,583
That's just how it is...

239
00:16:25,666 --> 00:16:27,666
in this world of ours.

240
00:16:44,166 --> 00:16:46,583
So what happened?

241
00:16:46,666 --> 00:16:49,291
Well Priscilla and Clare
fought and Isley of the North

242
00:16:49,375 --> 00:16:51,708
showed his face before
they both disappeared...

243
00:16:51,791 --> 00:16:54,750
I assume that's all the
explanation that you'll need.

244
00:16:54,833 --> 00:16:56,125
Is she dead?

245
00:16:57,541 --> 00:16:59,375
I can't sense her aura...

246
00:16:59,458 --> 00:17:02,166
That's all I can say
with certainty...

247
00:17:02,250 --> 00:17:03,458
If you want to know...

248
00:17:03,541 --> 00:17:05,375
go see for yourself.

249
00:17:05,458 --> 00:17:06,875
That's true...

250
00:17:06,958 --> 00:17:08,708
I may.

251
00:17:10,333 --> 00:17:12,416
Or at least I would like to...

252
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:14,166
But it won't happen...

253
00:17:14,250 --> 00:17:17,083
Besides, I already have
my hands full dealing

254
00:17:17,166 --> 00:17:19,708
with the carnage in Pieta.

255
00:17:21,666 --> 00:17:23,291
