is going to be okay...?

258
00:17:36,625 --> 00:17:38,166
She was so depressed
it looked like her soul

259
00:17:38,250 --> 00:17:40,583
had been ripped out.

260
00:17:40,666 --> 00:17:43,500
Whether she dies tomorrow
or lives to old age...

261
00:17:43,583 --> 00:17:45,583
it's all in Clare's hands now.

262
00:17:45,666 --> 00:17:48,208
Besides, it's none
of our business.

263
00:17:48,291 --> 00:17:49,250
Yeah.

264
00:17:49,333 --> 00:17:51,625
I guess you're right.

265
00:17:51,708 --> 00:17:54,500
Let's part ways here.

266
00:17:54,583 --> 00:17:55,916
That's a good idea.

267
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:56,833
Wait...

268
00:17:56,916 --> 00:17:58,375
So what are you
going to do now?

269
00:18:00,416 --> 00:18:03,083
My plan is to leave
the Organization...

270
00:18:03,166 --> 00:18:04,375
and then train hard...

271
00:18:04,458 --> 00:18:06,541
so that I can
have revenge someday.

272
00:18:06,625 --> 00:18:08,625
And I intend to do the same...

273
00:18:08,708 --> 00:18:11,416
I'm determined to reveal all of
the secrets the Organization

274
00:18:11,500 --> 00:18:12,750
has been hiding...

275
00:18:12,833 --> 00:18:14,166
I'll live among the
civilians until

276
00:18:14,250 --> 00:18:15,916
I have sufficient evidence.

277
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:18,375
That sounds incredibly boring.

278
00:18:18,458 --> 00:18:19,500
Oh...

279
00:18:19,583 --> 00:18:21,166
Have something more
exciting planned?

280
00:18:21,250 --> 00:18:23,791
I'll be damned if I work for
the Organization again...

281
00:18:23,875 --> 00:18:25,333
so...

282
00:18:25,416 --> 00:18:27,208
I don't know.

283
00:18:27,291 --> 00:18:29,500
Well you know you can
always tag along with me.

284
00:18:29,583 --> 00:18:30,750
Sure...

