00:18:30,833 --> 00:18:32,041
I mean you're not going
to get very far trying

286
00:18:32,125 --> 00:18:33,583
to spar with yourself...

287
00:18:33,666 --> 00:18:35,416
Plus I could use the company.

288
00:18:38,166 --> 00:18:40,333
I guess this is
goodbye my friends.

289
00:18:43,291 --> 00:18:45,458
Though I can't say when...

290
00:18:45,541 --> 00:18:46,958
we'll meet again.

291
00:18:47,041 --> 00:18:48,625
I'm sure.

292
00:18:48,708 --> 00:18:50,250
You better believe it.

293
00:18:53,375 --> 00:18:55,208
Same goes for her.

294
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,750
Don't you forget...

295
00:19:05,833 --> 00:19:10,208
There are people in this world
that want to see you live...

296
00:19:10,291 --> 00:19:13,625
And there are those who
have put their faith in you.

297
00:19:16,166 --> 00:19:17,250
Just live...

298
00:19:17,333 --> 00:19:18,916
Please live.

299
00:19:27,208 --> 00:19:28,458
Something wrong?

300
00:19:28,541 --> 00:19:30,625
I apologize that
it took this long...

301
00:19:30,708 --> 00:19:32,291
to find you.

302
00:19:32,375 --> 00:19:34,625
I'm proud of you
for staying safe.

303
00:19:34,708 --> 00:19:37,166
That couldn't have been easy.

304
00:19:37,250 --> 00:19:41,500
I have no intention of returning
to work for the Organization.

305
00:19:41,583 --> 00:19:42,750
Just know...

306
00:19:42,833 --> 00:19:45,833
The journey will be more
difficult than before.

307
00:19:45,916 --> 00:19:47,000
So...

308
00:19:47,083 --> 00:19:48,541
Will you join me?

309
00:19:50,583 --> 00:19:52,833
Clare.

310
00:19:52,916 --> 00:19:54,708
Of course...

311
00:19:54,791 --> 00:19:56,250
I...

312
00:19:56,333 --> 00:19:58,083
I never want to leave you!

313
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:04,000
Thank you, Raki.

314
00:20:47,791 --> 00:20:49,000
Teresa...

315
00:20:49,083 --> 00:20:51,416
I'm still alive...

316
00:20:51,500 --> 00:20:55,625
I can almost hear you say,
"That's the way it should be."

317
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:16,500
Live as a human...

318
00:21:16,583 --> 00:21:18,416
Grow as a human...

319
00:21:18,500 --> 00:21:21,375
Die a human death.

320
00:21:21,458 --> 00:21:25,625
This is the greatest gift that
I can possibly give to you...

321
00:21:25,708 --> 00:21:27,208
So use it well.

322
00:21:29,166 --> 00:21:31,750
Farewell, Clare.

